parameters: “Reincarnated person, first please tell me your name.”
"The mission given to you is to save this world."
“Right now, this world is facing a crisis.”
"Humans always fight and kill each other in the three kingdoms."
"You will be the one who brings harmony to this world."
“From the moment I started, I was suddenly entrusted with something amazing…”
"I don't feel like I can handle such a heavy responsibility..."
"First of all, let's imagine what you look like when you live in this world."
“Then I will create you as a reincarnated person in this form.”
“...And you seem like a person with talent.”
"Let me give you this, I'm sure it will be useful."
"What's this? It's written about the conditions for the event to occur..."
“Will I get anything from this event?
I don't really know, but if you think you can meet the conditions, give it a try.''
"From now on, you will descend on Arya, the neutral city of Midgard."
“There are friends of ours in the world beyond.”
“It would be a good idea to learn a lot of things at the Reincarnated Mansion first.”
"I pray that you will become the savior of this world."
#Reincarnation! It's like a dark light effect.
